																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">4</div> <div class="vers-content">Now Joakim was very rich, and had an orchard near his house: and the Jews resorted to him, because he was the most honourable of them all.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">4</div> <div class="vers-content">A rich man was Joakim, and had a fruit-garden close to his house; and he was much visited by the Jews, among whom there was none more honoured than he.</div></div></td>
