																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">7</div> <div class="vers-content">And when the people departed away at noon, Susanna went in, and walked in her husbandâ€™s orchard.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">7</div> <div class="vers-content">At noon, when the common folk had returned home, Susanna would walk about in her husbandâ€™s garden,</div></div></td>
