								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">21</div> <div class="vers-content">Quod si nolueris, dicemus contra te testimonium, quod fuerit tecum juvenis, et ob hanc causam emiseris puellas a te.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">21</div> <div class="vers-content">But if thou wilt not, we will bear witness against thee, that a young man was with thee, and therefore thou didst send away thy maids from thee.</div></div></td>
